const dotenv = require('dotenv').config; import nodemailer from 'nodemailer'; let sendSimpleEmail = async (emailData) => { const transporter = nodemailer.createTransport({ host: "smtp.gmail.com", port: 587, secure: false, // true for port 465, false for other ports auth: { user: process.env.EMAIL_APP, pass: process.env.EMAIL_APP_PASSWORD, }, }); // send mail with defined transport object const info = await transporter.sendMail({ from: '"t lch khm bnh" ', // sender address to: emailData.receiverEmail, // list of receivers subject: "Thng tin t lch khm bnh", // Subject line // attachments: [{ // filename: 'logo.png', // path: '../FE/src/assets/logo.png', // cid: 'logo' // }], html: createHTMLContent_test(emailData, emailData.language), }); } // style = "color : black ; display : flex ; flex-direction : column" //createHTMLContent(emailData, emailData.language) let createHTMLContent = (emailData, language) => { if (language === 'vi') return (`

Xin cho ${emailData.patientName}

Bn nhn c email ny v t lch khm bnh online trn : bookingcare.com

Thng tin t lch khm bnh:

Thi gian: ${emailData.date}

Bc s m nhim: ${emailData.doctorName}

Nu thng tin ny l tht xin vui lng click vo ng link bn di xc nhn v hon tt th tc khm bnh

Xc nhn lch hn `) else { return (`

Hello ${emailData.patientName}

You received this email as you have booked a schedule : bookingcare.com

booking informations:

Time: ${emailData.date}

Doctor: ${emailData.doctorName}

In case all the informations above are correct, please click the link below to confirm and redirect to complete booking form

Confirm booking
`) } } let createHTMLContent_test = (emailData, language) => { if (language === 'vi') { return ( `
We're thrilled to have you here! Get ready to dive into your new account.

Th xc nhn lch khm

Xin cho ${emailData.patientName}

Bn nhn c email ny v t lch khm bnh online trn : bookingcare.com

Thng tin t lch khm bnh:

Thi gian: ${emailData.date}

Bc s m nhim: ${emailData.doctorName}

Nu thng tin ny l tht xin vui lng click vo ng link bn di xc nhn v hon tt th tc khm bnh
Xc nhn lch khm

Nu cn h tr hy tr li trc tip ti email ny hoc gi theo hotline: 0123-231-123-321.

Cheer,
BaoDuy

iu khon v dch v ca bookingcare

Policy & Copyright

Ton b thng tin c lm mang tnh cht gi nh vui lng lin h facebook chnh ch c h tr hoc trao i.
` ) } else { return ( `
We're thrilled to have you here! Get ready to dive into your new account.

Letter confrim booking schedule

Hello ${emailData.patientName}

You received this email as you have booked a schedule : bookingcare.com

booking informations:

Time: ${emailData.date}

Doctor: ${emailData.doctorName}

In case all the informations above are correct, please click the link below to confirm and redirect to complete booking form
Confirm booking

In case you need support please directly reply this email or call hotline: 0123-231-123-321.

Cheer,
BaoDuy

policy and copyright of bookingcare

Policy & Copyright

All informations above just for simulation,contact facebook author in case need support.
` ) } } {/* this is logo */ } module.exports = { sendSimpleEmail }
